>> time required: 2 hours
>> course: main

Combine @garlic cloves{4}, @asian pear{1%cup}, @onion{0.75%cups}, and @ginger{1%tsp} in blender until smooth
Add @soy sauce{2%tbsp}, @brown sugar{1%tbsp}, @sesame oil{1%tbsp}
Pour mixture into large bowl with thinly sliced @beef skirt steak{500%g}, @green onions{3}, matchstick cut @carrot{1}, sliced @onion{1}
Let marinate at least ~{30%minutes} up to several hours
Heat cast iron pan or use charcoal fire to cook meat for a couple minutes
